statement.p:
Evaluate the function.
    f(x)=\begin{cases}
        4 \amp  x \lt 1\\
        5+2x-x^2  \amp  1\le x\lt 3\\
        2x \amp  x \gt 3
        \end{cases}

image.latex-image:

\tikzset{%
}
\begin{tikzpicture} [scale=.5]
\draw[cyan] (-4,0) grid (4,8);
\draw[black,thick, ->, >=stealth'] (-4,0)--(4.6,0) node[right]{$x$};
\draw[black,thick, ->, >=stealth'] (0,0)--(0,8.6) node[above]{$y$};
\foreach \x in {-2,-4,2,4} {
  \draw[black,thick] (\x,.1)--++(0,-.2) node[below, fill=white, inner sep=1, yshift=-2]{\x};
}
\foreach \x in {2,4,6,8} {
  \draw[black,thick] (.1,\x)--++(-.2,0) node[left, fill=white, inner sep=1, xshift=-2]{\x};
}

\draw[red, very thick] (-4,4) -- (1,4);
\draw[red, thick, fill=white,opacity=1] (1,4) circle (.1);

\draw[red, thick, fill=red] (1,6) circle (.1);
\draw[samples=65,domain=1:3,smooth,variable=\x,red,very thick] plot ({\x},{5+2*\x-(\x)^2});
\draw[red, thick, fill=white,opacity=1] (3,2) circle (.1);

\draw[red, thick] (3,6) -- (4,8);
\draw[red, thick, fill=white,opacity=1] (3,6) circle (.1);
\end{tikzpicture}

statement.p:
Sketch a graph of the function, and evaluate for the inputs below.
    g(x)=\begin{cases}
        x+2 \amp  x \lt -1\\
        1  \amp  -1\lt x\lt 1\\
        x \amp  x \ge 1
        \end{cases}

image.latex-image:

\tikzset{%
}
\begin{tikzpicture} [scale=.5]
\draw[cyan] (-4,-4) grid (4,4);
\draw[black,thick, ->, >=stealth'] (-4,0)--(4.6,0) node[right]{$x$};
\draw[black,thick, ->, >=stealth'] (0,-4)--(0,4.6) node[above]{$y$};
\foreach \x in {-2,-4,2,4} {
  \draw[black,thick] (\x,.1)--++(0,-.2) node[below, fill=white, inner sep=1, yshift=-2]{\x};
  \draw[black,thick] (.1,\x)--++(-.2,0) node[left, fill=white, inner sep=1, xshift=-2]{\x};
}

\draw[red, thick] (-4,-2) -- (-1,1) -- (1,1) -- (4,4);
\draw[red, thick, fill=white,opacity=1] (-1,1) circle (.1);
\draw[red, thick, fill=red] (1,1) circle (.1);
\end{tikzpicture}
